#: ../../language/error_codes/E4120.md:1
msgid "E4120"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4120.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `unhandled_error`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`unhandled_error`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4120.md:5
msgid "The application might raise errors, but they are not handled."
msgstr "该函数应用可能会引发错误，但这些错误没有被处理。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4120.md:7
msgid ""
"Current MoonBit reports the ordinary unhandled re-raise pattern as "
"[E4122](./E4122.md). This page is retained for older compiler output that"
" used E4120 with the deprecated postfix error-handling syntax."
msgstr ""
"当前 MoonBit 会将普通的未处理重新抛出模式报告为 "
"[E4122](./E4122.md)。本页面保留给较旧编译器输出使用；旧版编译器会针对已弃用的后缀错误处理语法报告 E4120。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4120.md:11
msgid ""
"In MoonBit, we require programmers to explicitly annotate which functions"
" may raise errors. A function that re-raises an error must use a `raise` "
"annotation in its signature. To keep the current function from raising, "
"handle the error with `try ... catch`. If the `Result[T, E]` value must "
"escape the local expression, build it explicitly with `Ok` and `Err` in "
"the `try ... catch` branches."
msgstr ""
"在 MoonBit 中，程序员需要显式标注哪些函数可能引发错误。重新抛出错误的函数必须在签名中使用 `raise` "
"标注。若要让当前函数不抛出错误，请使用 `try ... catch` 处理错误。如果 `Result[T, E]` "
"值必须逃逸出局部表达式，请在 `try ... catch` 分支中用 `Ok` 和 `Err` 显式构造它。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4120.md:18
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4120.md:20
msgid ""
"See [E4122](./E4122.md) for checked erroneous examples with the current "
"syntax."
msgstr "当前语法下已检查的错误示例请参阅 [E4122](./E4122.md)。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4120.md:22
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4120.md:24
msgid "You can either annotate the caller so it re-raises the error:"
msgstr "您可以为调用者添加标注，使其重新抛出错误："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4120.md:26
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub suberror ExampleError {\n"
"  Failed\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"pub fn may_raise_error(input : Int) -> Unit raise ExampleError {\n"
"  if input == 42 {\n"
"    return\n"
"  }\n"
"  raise Failed\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"pub fn caller() -> Unit raise ExampleError {\n"
"  may_raise_error(42)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4120.md:30
msgid "Or materialize the error to a `Result[T, E]` type with `try ... catch`:"
msgstr "或者使用 `try ... catch` 将错误物化为 `Result[T, E]` 类型："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4120.md:32
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub fn materialize_error() -> Result[Unit, ExampleError] {\n"
"  try {\n"
"    may_raise_error(42)\n"
"    Ok(())\n"
"  } catch {\n"
"    error => Err(error)\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
